org.batfish.coordinator

Class WorkMgrServiceV2

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.batfish.coordinator.WorkMgrServiceV2

  • @Path(value="/v2")
 @Produces(value="application/json")
public class WorkMgrServiceV2
extends java.lang.Object
    The Work Manager is a RESTful service for servicing client API calls.

    The Work Manager provides information about the containers, testrigs, questions, and analyses in the Batfish service based on the credentials of the client, and provides authenticated clients the ability to create/delete or otherwise modify the same.
